'''Danny Minahan''' is the son of [[Ashley Minahan]].

==History==
Danny came to the practice with his parents and his two brothers when their mom was pregnant. She was just there for a checkup, but stayed when Addison told her she was in labor. She gave birth to another boy.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
Danny is one of four boys.
